---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const lang = "en";
---

<BaseLayout
  lang={lang}
  title="Programs – Le Ballon Rouge"
  description="Ministry-approved French-language programs in Hamilton and Brantford. Toddler, preschool and before/after school care focused on play and exploration."
>

  <!-- Page intro -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-10 pt-8 md:pt-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-5xl">Programs</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-prose text-base font-medium leading-7 text-slate-600 md:text-lg">
      Ministry-approved French-language programs focused on exploration and play.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a
        href="/en/inscription/"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-white shadow-lg shadow-red-700/20 hover:bg-red-800"
      >
        How to register
      </a>
      <a
        href="#enonce"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:bg-white"
      >
        Program Statement
      </a>
      <a
        href="#qualite"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:bg-white"
      >
        Quality
      </a>
      <a
        href="#evenements"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:bg-white"
      >
        Events
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Program cards -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-12">
    <div class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-2xl">Our programs</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        All programs at La Garderie Française de Hamilton Inc. are licensed. We hold a permit recognized by the Ministry of Education and
        our programs are subject to inspections (Ministry and health unit) for the renewal of our operating licences.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        We hire staff trained in early childhood education and maintain the child-to-educator ratios required by law across all our programs.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black">Toddler</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
            <span class="font-extrabold">Growing at Le Ballon Rouge</span> — Ready or not, here I come! All my senses are awake to explore, feel,
            taste and understand the world around me. At Le Ballon Rouge, I am welcomed with warmth and encouraged to discover at my own pace.
            I express myself more and more, I form my first sentences and I am already showing my personality. Every day I get to learn new things
            and explore new abilities. Even when things get a little messy, it's always filled with joy, creativity and growth.
            I just need a little guidance… but I'm pretty sure the right direction leads to the playground!
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black">Preschool</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
            <span class="font-extrabold">Ready to explore!</span> I am encouraged to discover the world around me. I develop my first skills by
            expressing myself, handling objects, imitating gestures and observing the world with wonder. At Le Ballon Rouge, I build habits that
            make me more independent: I dress myself; I use tools and materials (like scissors); I organize myself in simple tasks,
            which helps me build confidence and take on new challenges. Every day I feel ready to learn and try new things,
            guided by caring adults.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black">Before & After School</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
            <span class="font-extrabold">Exploring new horizons</span> — I'm curious to discover new things before and after school,
            explore activities and make friends! In the before/after school program, I get to engage in enriching activities
            that broaden my horizons. Whether it's creative play, sports, music or art, every moment is a chance to explore my talents
            and build my confidence. I am surrounded by caring adults who help me grow, thrive and discover what I'm passionate about.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Program Statement -->
  <section id="enonce" class="scroll-mt-28 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-12">
    <div class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-2xl">Program Statement</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        At Le Ballon Rouge, all staff members are required to review the program statement when they are hired and again every year.
        It serves as a reference tool that ensures consistency across the centre and informs parents of the educational approach chosen.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        The program statement outlines the approaches applied by staff (and prohibited practices), and specifies the measures taken in cases
        of non-compliance.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-5">
        <p class="font-extrabold">Option (recommended):</p>
        <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
          Add a download button linking to a PDF version of the statement (to be hosted later), or paste an abbreviated web version here.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/docs/enonce-de-programme.pdf"
          class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold shadow-sm hover:bg-white/80"
        >
          Download the statement (PDF)
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quality -->
  <section id="qualite" class="scroll-mt-28 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-12">
    <div class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-2xl">Quality</h2>

      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        Our childcare centre participates in quality measurement programs and tools to continuously reflect on and improve our practices:
        <span class="font-extrabold">Fostering Brant's Growth</span> (Brantford) and <span class="font-extrabold">System Priority</span> (Hamilton).
      </p>

      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        Each staff member maintains a continuous professional learning plan grounded in self-reflection; the centre requires a minimum of
        four professional development events per year (January to December). Staff are also familiarized with the document
        "How Does Learning Happen? Ontario's Pedagogy for the Early Years."
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black">Healthy and safe environment</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
            We follow health and safety standards set by municipal, provincial and federal bodies, and conduct regular follow-ups
            using checklists and inspections.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black">Support and inclusion</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
            Resource consultants (e.g. Lansdowne Children's Centre, Community Living) may visit our centres to provide support to staff,
            children and families; children with special needs can be integrated into the program with a positive and welcoming approach.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Events -->
  <section id="evenements" class="scroll-mt-28 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-12">
    <div class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-2xl">Events</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 max-w-prose leading-7 text-slate-600">
            At Le Ballon Rouge, we love creating opportunities for children, families and team members to come together, celebrate and have fun.
            Throughout the year, we organize a variety of events (seasonal celebrations, theme days, performances, creative workshops, and more).
          </p>
        </div>

        <a
          href="/en/inscription/"
          class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-700 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-extrabold text-white shadow-lg shadow-red-700/20 hover:bg-red-800 md:mt-0"
        >
          How to register
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Event timeline -->
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-5">

        <!-- Event 1 -->
        <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-[26px] border border-black/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/80 to-red-50/60 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-black/5 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/10">
          <div class="absolute -right-12 -top-12 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-red-700/10 blur-2xl"></div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-start md:gap-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-red-700/20 bg-white shadow-sm">
                <span aria-hidden="true" class="text-xl">🎈</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">Start of year</p>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">Welcome to Le Ballon Rouge</h3>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="leading-7 text-slate-600">
                A welcome activity to ease the transition, build a first connection with the team and discover the daily life of the centre
                in a warm and French-language setting.
              </p>

              <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs font-extrabold">
                <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-slate-700">For: families & children</span>
                <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-slate-700">Goal: building connections</span>
                <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-slate-700">Style: friendly & relaxed</span>
              </div>

              <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 font-semibold text-slate-700">
                <li>Meet the team and tour the spaces.</li>
                <li>Mini play activities and discovery corners for children.</li>
                <li>Practical info: routines, communications and partnerships.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Event 2 -->
        <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-[26px] border border-black/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/80 to-orange-50/70 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-black/5 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/10">
          <div class="absolute -right-12 -top-12 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-orange-500/10 blur-2xl"></div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-start md:gap-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-orange-500/20 bg-white shadow-sm">
                <span aria-hidden="true" class="text-xl">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">Seasonal</p>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">Family Celebration</h3>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="leading-7 text-slate-600">
                A moment to highlight the importance of our partnership with parents, strengthen our sense of community and create shared memories.
              </p>

              <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs font-extrabold">
                <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-slate-700">For: extended families</span>
                <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-slate-700">Activities: creative & playful</span>
                <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-slate-700">Atmosphere: festive</span>
              </div>

              <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 font-semibold text-slate-700">
                <li>Creative workshops (crafts, painting, collages).</li>
                <li>Cooperative games and outdoor activities (weather permitting).</li>
                <li>"Memory" corner: children's photos and artwork (depending on programming).</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Event 3 -->
        <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-[26px] border border-black/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/80 to-slate-50 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-black/5 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/10">
          <div class="absolute -right-12 -top-12 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-slate-500/10 blur-2xl"></div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-start md:gap-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-slate-400/20 bg-white shadow-sm">
                <span aria-hidden="true" class="text-xl">🎓</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">End of year</p>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">Preschool Graduation</h3>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="leading-7 text-slate-600">
                A celebration that honours the journey of our preschool children, highlights their achievements and marks a positive
                transition to the next chapter.
              </p>

              <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs font-extrabold">
                <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-slate-700">For: preschoolers</span>
                <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-slate-700">Focus: pride & confidence</span>
                <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-slate-700">Memories: photos & moments</span>
              </div>

              <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 font-semibold text-slate-700">
                <li>Small ceremony celebrating each child.</li>
                <li>Songs, stories or a short presentation (depending on the group).</li>
                <li>Celebration moment with families.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-5">
        <p class="font-extrabold text-slate-900">Note</p>
        <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
          Events vary by centre, group and time of year. Details (date/time) are communicated to families as they become available.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>